$_HOAM_language ['help_popups']['config']['user']['flags']['days_before_disable'] = '<h1>Old Password Stored</h1><p>This flag is only used when HOAM changes its method of storing passwords. If a new method is available, this flag will automatically be set for all of the users during the installation of a new version of HOAM.</p><p>This type of change will only occur if a security flaw is found in the existing password storage mechanism, and a newer method has been implemented.</p>'; 
