$_HOAM_language ['help_popups']['group']['ids']['admin'] = '<h1>System Administrators</h1>' . $_HOAM_language ['help_pages']['generic']['no_changes'] . '<p>This group is used to identify the users having System Administrator privileges. Typically only the Root and System users should be members of this group.</p><p>Select the checkbox to enable this field for editing.</p>';
